I am pretty sure that MILNET hosts are required to use a hosts
official name, e.g., "ALMSA-1.ARPA".  

I think that MILNET hosts are required to use domain style names, but
not required (yet) to use name servers.  So i think it is appropriate
to discuss and schedule the elimination of all non-domain style names
from the HOSTS.TXT file and the Internet.

--jon.
